public enum BdewLoadProfile
extends java.lang.Enum<BdewLoadProfile>
implements StandardLoadProfile
German standard electricity load profiles, defined by the bdew (Bundesverband der Energie- und Wasserwirtschaft; engl.Federal Association of the Energy and Water Industry). For more details see https://www.bdew.de/energie/standardlastprofile-strom/
